company_name: KF- PET FOOD - TIERNAHRUNGS- VERTRIEBSGESELLSCHAFT MBH
information: The company KF- PET FOOD - TIERNAHRUNGS- VERTRIEBSGESELLSCHAFT MBH, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1991, which operates in the Dog food industry. It also operates in the Cat food industries. It is based in Kastellaun, Germany.
